## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the complexity of quantifying the full economic impact of pollution. Additionally, the effectiveness of proposed solutions varies across different regions and industries, making it challenging to generalize findings globally. Further research is needed to explore innovative approaches to mitigating pollution and achieving sustainable economic development.

